{"tid":1456843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認同既share開去 我識政府個編劇","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:55:44.000Z","uid":254961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f27b094a11293c7f52487b3976e7a75793a9e9","tid":1456843,"uid":254961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"政府理想劇本 ： <br />\n機場手足走唔曬 比狗打 比狗拉 仲要好過分咁打 屠殺 <br />\n已經撤左既手足 太嬲 衝動 忍唔到手 /比鬼帶風向 <br />\n去圍狗屋或圍政總/......<br />\n又再打過 <br />\n打完 無狗傷 無傷害到政府 <br />\n但我地手足損傷一大堆 <br />\n之後鬼/和理非話要休息 比勇武抖<br />\n聽日我地可能無力搞機場 <br />\n或者變左 和你飛嘉年華 <br />\n<br />\n我地理想劇本 ： <br />\n開開心心番屋企 聽日再去機場 <br />\n日日去 去到2046 <br />\n每日塞 機場每日跪低幾個鐘都好"},{"pid":"cfb4f13bb726a6758be2a9be0c557eb3ec1b1d08","tid":1456843,"uid":254961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子   奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴    驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span>城安<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyZ8fu3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyZ8fu3.gif&h=3c352850&s={SIZE}\" />夫<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6MuKoo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6MuKoo.gif&h=c58c6292&s={SIZE}\" />履<span style=\"color: gold;\">革</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span>國兒女   爾汝天<span style=\"color: gold;\">命</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"ba7a1e7c4b3150e6e9d80b0026c293551af2ec73","tid":1456843,"uid":254961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子   奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴    驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">